text: Nandrolone caproate (brand name Anabolin Depot), or nandrolone hexanoate, also known as 19-nortestosterone 17β-hexanoate, is a synthetic androgen and anabolic steroid and a nandrolone ester. ==See also== * List of androgen esters § Nandrolone esters ==References== Category:Androgens and anabolic steroids Category:Caproate esters Category:Estranes Category:Nandrolone esters Category:Progestogens Category:Testosterone
title: Nandrolone caproate
